  </section>

  <section class="split-block">
    <div class="split-grid">
      <div>
        <h2 class="section-heading">What belongs here</h2>
        <p class="section-copy">
          Use this space for the enduring explanation of mission, partners, origin,
          governance, and why the community approach matters.
        </p>
      </div>
      <ul class="plain-list">
        <li>Mission and field context</li>
        <li>Values and governance</li>
        <li>Institutional partners</li>
        <li>Funding and stewardship</li>
        <li>How AI4RA relates to the open source ecosystem</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
